                     <interp inst="t18240603-154-person1344" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a boot-maker. I was turning my horse into the field and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the baby's neck; he got over some bricks, and I took hold of him, and took the handkerchief from his pocket.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240603-154-person1345">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MERRY
               <interp inst="t18240603-154-person1345" type="surname" value="MERRY"></interp>
